.<br /><br />To bag on the level 58 and 61 necro's who happened to find everquest later than you is not only lame but funny to me.  I'm sure that if they had a tutor they could pass you in a month with your 3 day a week playing style.  Granted it was annoying how they mixed up quotes and put words in your mouth.  I don't like the "attack every uber who posts here mentality" either, but the fact is, it was a discussion till you started with the "thank you drive through and your dismissed."  Then it turned into a feeding frenzy on every detail of your life. You treat people like yard trash/plebians, expect to be hated like an aristocrat.  <br /><br />I don't have my magelo attached to my sig, but just in case you want it, 37962.  I'm not uber, but wise enough to know where i stand on the totem pole.  Enough with this i'm gonna go play some more<br /><br />Leriche</span></font></td>
